<p class="font_8" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Otherwise, mainly if you have what it takes resulting to you being scouted.</span></p></div><div id="comp-kob1b0x4" class="_1Q9if" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_2" style="font-size:44px;"><span style="font-style:normal;"><span style="font-family:avenir-lt-w01_85-heavy1475544,sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight:400;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><span style="font-size:46px;">Art Team</span></span></span></span></span></h2></div><div id="comp-kob1c1g9" class="_1Q9if" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">An artist for the server that generally provides server art, such as emotes. Using digital technology as part of the creative or presentation process.</span></p>

