&nbsp;</p></div><div id="comp-kob1fg1q" class="_1Q9if" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_2" style="font-size:40px;"><span style="font-style:normal;"><span style="font-family:avenir-lt-w01_85-heavy1475544,sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight:400;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><span style="font-size:46px;">Lore Team</span></span></span></span></span></h2></div><div id="comp-kob1ga6x" class="_1Q9if" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">A team dedicated for WFPs various lore projects. Currently we're working on getting a database set up, but we hope to be producing a variety of lore-based content in collaboration with WFP's other media teams. Working to establish a team capable of creating a well-sourced, in-depth collection of content exploring Genshin Impact's wide range of lore.</span></p>

<p class="font_8" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Members joining this team are recommended to have:<br>
- Writing proficiency is definitely essential. Being able to clearly express your points and make your arguments at a consistently high quality.<br>
- Familiarity with Notion, Google Sheets/Docs, and other writing/collaborative software.<br>
- Attention to detail, able to make logical and clear connections between various pieces of lore in their writing.<br>
- Good behavior. This means being able to produce constructive criticism of other's writing and speculation, and being respectful in the event of disagreements in interpretation.<br>
- While not required, visual presentation skills are always a bonus to have. Lore that looks good reads good!</span></p>

<p class="font_8" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Otherwise, mainly if you are an active contributor and show the above behavior, we may reach out and scout you for the team.</span></p></div><div id="comp-kob1qr9m" class="_1Q9if" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_2" style="font-size:40px;"><span style="font-style:normal;"><span style="font-family:avenir-lt-w01_85-heavy1475544,sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight:400;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><span style="font-size:46px;">Theorycrafting Team</span></span></span></span></span></h2></div><div id="comp-kob1s1bd" class="_1Q9if" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">The staff team for the server's theorycrafting section. From handling theorycrafting related leaks, moderating theorycrafting channels, to peer reviewing and writing guide, we deal with all things Genshin math and optimization related.</span></p>

<p class="font_8" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">When we open application, we will aim for applicants with these skillsets:<br>
- Good game knowledge, understanding of in-depth game concepts and mechanics.<br>
